text.tspan: AYNI WAS CREATED OUT OF A COMMON LOVE FOR HIGH QUALITY PRODUCTS,
NATURE’S FINEST MATERIALS AND STRONG SOCIAL, ECONOMIC AND ENVIROMENTAL
THE PRODUCTS ARE CREATED IN PERU, A COUNTRY WITH ONE OF THE WORLDS
FASTEST GROWING ECONOMIES, USING ONLY THE MOST EXCLUSIVE PERUVIAN
MATERIALS SUCH AS THE LUXURIOUS BABY ALPACA AND THE FAMOUS PIMA COTTON.
THROUGH AYNI WE SEEK TO SET AN EXAMPLE TO THE REST OF THE FASHION AND
APPAREL INDUSTRY BY SHOWING HOW ETHICS AND AESTHETICS CAN JOIN HANDS
AND ENCOURAGE TO A MORE CONSCIENCE LIFE STYLE AND CONSUMPTION.
